{"tid":492164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【怪癖「喪屍」】拐子佬噬男童屁股 自己甩咗2隻牙","createTime":"2017-12-07T09:22:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T09:29:34.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"854e4c8b8934843638d965f9e030460eeb6b839c","tid":492164,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:22:03.000Z","msg":"福建龍海一名男子昨（6日）突然發狂，猶如「喪屍」出沒。他試圖搶走一個正與母親在巴士站等車的男童，更捉住男童，餓虎擒羊般向男童的屁股啃咬，咬完還掉了2顆牙齒。警方指男子行動怪異，動機不明，已把他拘捕。<br />\n警方指，涉事男子姓陳，32歲，是雲南大理人。他在巴士站企圖搶走一名男童，還張口咬傷男童屁股，他遭附近好心人制服在地上時才鬆口，還掉了2顆牙齒，地上有懷疑是他的血迹。男童得救後疑受驚不淺，哇哇大哭久久未停。<br />\n警方指男子行為怪異，動機不明，已拘捕他續查案件。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171207&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57548204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171207%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57548204&d=kWCJKjsukCZ1LztrjtSwCjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=01931bd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171207%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57548204&h=ad1f6ecd\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171207&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57548204</a>"},{"pid":"5554851c508ccd717acb2024f736577150d851ad","tid":492164,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"感染左啦"},{"pid":"4a66ea357a9bd9c57414e255165efe6d5e3bd031","tid":492164,"uid":89449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"中國會唔會傳染d喪屍病毒黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cc756b4ca40eac8423659e4785508249a6abd8","tid":492164,"uid":73262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"細路個屎忽先勁  喪屍都咬唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}